{"tid":1536880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"柴灣小西灣group召集記者明早7：00到中基採訪","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:14:21.000Z","uid":34047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6802ffe6ea89e5a119d899ce27f99bdfcdd6d7","tid":1536880,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:42:42.000Z","msg":"轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#記者會 #pressconference<br />\n<br />\n現召集各方傳媒於明天早上7:00到中華基金中學外進行採訪， 校方明確阻撓罷課， 並揚言會將罷課學生退學，亦已有老師證實明天學校叫喚防暴警察到學校門外對學生進行搜身。<br />\n日期：9月4日<br />\n時間：上午7時正<br />\n地點：中華基金中學（柴灣小西灣富欣道9號）<br />\n<br />\nCalling on media to report on and conduct interviews at The Chinese Foundation Secondary School at 7:00am tomorrow morning. The school management has attempted to obstruct the strike, and declared that it will expel striking students. Teachers verified that the school will call on riot police forces to search students outside school gates. <br />\nDay: 4th September <br />\nTime: 7:00am<br />\nLocation: The Chinese Foundation Secondary School (9 Harmony Rd, Siu Sai Wan, Hong Kong)"},{"pid":"974a6b058d719b774001c5902acb30694721b9c8","tid":1536880,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e9757c0df966ee4afe1d6cecf91403dbc22f4d","tid":1536880,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有